        "subject": "LU-4442 mdt: check version for the child in mdt_reint_link",
        "message": "LU-4442 mdt: check version for the child in mdt_reint_link\n\nIn mdt_reint_link(), do version check for the child before\ncalling mdt_object_exists(), so that if the child object does not\nexist, the client can be evicted correctly.\n\nTest-Parameters: testlist=replay-vbr envdefinitions=SLOW=yes,ONLY=7g\nSigned-off-by: Emoly Liu <emoly.liu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5bcb2c5e2f854750541fc8dbaa7c38a94c0cb342\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
